ef=\"http://www.ioactive.com/pdfs/IOActive_Car_Hacking_Poories.pdf\">Car Hacking on the Cheap</a> -  A whitepaper from Chris Valasek and IOActive on hacking your car when you don't have a lot of resources at your disposal.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-08-24T14:07:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://phys.org/news/2017-05-tackle-autonomous-vehicle.html\">Researchers tackle autonomous vehicle security</a> - Texas A&#x26;M researchers develop intelligence system prototype.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-08-24T14:07:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h2>Articles</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://blog.quarkslab.com/reverse-engineering-of-the-nitro-obd2.html\">Reverse engineering of the Nitro OBD2</a> - Reverse engineering of CAN diagnostic tools.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-08-24T14:07:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h2>Presentations</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.blackhat.com/docs/eu-16/materials/eu-16-Sintsov-Pen-Testing-Vehicles-With-Cantoolz.pdf\">Pentesting vehicles with YACHT (Yet Another Car Hacking Tool)</a> -A presentation that discuesses different attack surfaces of a vehicle, then continues to describe an approach to car hacking along with tools needed to analyse and gather useful information.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-08-24T14:07:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h2>Presentations</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KU7gl1n1tIs\">How to drift with any car</a> - Introduction to CAN hacking, and using a real car as an Xbox controller.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-08-24T14:07:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"jaredthecoder/awesome-vehicle-security","categoryHTML":"<h2>Research Papers</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://illmatics.com/carhacking.html\">Miller and Valasek</a> - Self pro